## AGT.1.10 — Must be able to refer to the current values and change the settings of the proxy settings for connecting to the AdminLink server and the remote control settings on the "Advanced Settings" screen.

> 「詳細設定画面」でアドミリンクサーバー接続用のプロキシー設定と、遠隔操作に関する設定について現在値の参照と設定変更をできる事。


**Rationale:** 
- Client wants to use the proxy for access to the AdminLink server.
- Client wants to change the remote control settings.

### AGT.1.10.0 — Refer to the current value of the proxy server settings.
