### AGT.2.5.50 — Creating status JSON data
> ステータスJSONデータの作成


#### `AGT.2.5.51`

After all event checking is complete, if one or more events are detected and event JSON data is generated, status JSON data will be created.


<details><summary>日本語</summary>

