## AGT.2.6 — Must be able to send JSON data to the Adminlink server

> JSONデータをアドミリンクサーバーへ送信できる事


**Rationale:** Client wants to send any informations to the AdminLink server as JSON format.


### AGT.2.6.0 — Common specifications for JSON data
> JSONデータの共通仕様


#### `AGT.2.6.1`

The data format of the JSON data shall be as follows
Refer also to the sheet "Upload,Download Functions" on the document "EJ05.(AdminLink)for device side developmentRFP".


