#### `AGT.3.2.51`

Use the downloaded file to execute the process corresponding to the remote operation ID.
If the execution is successful, <Successful remote control processing of the downloaded file> shall be executed.
If execution fails, <Remote operation processing of downloaded file failed> should be executed.
In case of "Firmware Update (2010)", perform F/W update of the device with the downloaded "firmware" file.
For "Configuration Change (5070)," the downloaded "Configuration Data JSON" file is used to execute the device configuration change.
For "Configuration Restore (5080)", use the downloaded "Configuration Information" file (*.bin or *.cfg) to restore the device settings.


<details><summary>日本語</summary>

ダウンロードしたファイルを使い、遠隔操作IDに対応した処理を実行する。
