サーバーからの遠隔操作リクエストを受信した場合は、＜遠隔操作の受信＞（AGT.4.3.60）を実行すること。

</details>


- [ ] When a remote control request is received from the server, <Receive Remote Control> (AGT.4.3.60) shall be executed.


#### `AGT.4.3.13`

＜Execute "Judgment as to whether or not the setting has been changed" and "Judgment as to the expiration date of temporary registration" at 10 second intervals.


